laboratory_examinations.procedure_name: Liver function tests (ALT, AST, alkaline phosphatase, total bilirubin, gamma-glutamyltransferase, creatine kinase)
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Five days after start of remdesivir, an acute increase in ALT and AST was seen; following the discontinuation of remdesivir, ALT and AST values rapidly decreased to normal levels.
